  "system": {
    "description": {
      "value": "<p>Your mastery of the forge grants you special abilities:</p><p><strong>Resistance.</strong> You gain Resistance to Fire damage.</p><p><strong>Defense.</strong> While wearing Heavy Armor, you gain a +1 bonus to AC.</p><p><strong>Improved Mending.</strong> Your Mending cantrip now has a casting time of one action. Additionally, constructs or objects that have more than 0 Hit Points can spend up to your Wisdom modifier (minimum of 1) Hit Dice to regain Hit Points when they are the target of your Mending cantrip. If the target does not normally have Hit Dice, then they instead regain 1 Hit Point.</p>",
